 <h2 id="titreP" >Customer Loyalty Program</h2>  
 <hr id="ligne">
<p><a href="Customer_Loyalty_Program.htm" ><img  class="imageflottane" src="images/Customer Loyalty Program.jpg" alt="Customer Loyalty Program" Title="Customer Loyalty Program"/></a> <div id="imageleftparagraphe">Customer loyalty programs are a great way to retain and build your client base as well as build brand advocates. By offering your customers a loyalty program, you engage them and as a result your company builds longer business relationships.</div></p>

<p>There is a high perceived value in customer loyalty programs. When comparing products or services from competing brands, clients factor in added value services such as loyalty programs. If your company has a customer loyalty program, make sure it is properly marketed.</p>

<a class="lien" href="contactUs.htm" style="margin-left:20px;">Contact us to Build a Proprietary Customer Loyalty Program</a> 
<div class="paragraphe1" >
<h4 id="titre">Why Build a Proprietary Customer Loyalty Program</h4>  
<p class="paragraphe">As the consumer market evolves, companies seeking to capture more value will have to deepen their understanding of their customer's behavior  in order to segment their loyalty program offer. Proprietary customer loyalty programs that are segmented properly will generate repeat business from its clients leading to brand loyalty.</p><br>

<p>Proprietary customer loyalty programs encourage customers to interact directly with your brand whereas a coalition program would not . This translates into repeat brand exposure and increased communication opportunities.</p>
</div>

